{"_path":"/_lood/beebiloust-crypti-laul","_dir":"_lood","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Crypti laul","description":"Tänavad me vanemad, nad kodu ja kool on ka.","layout":"story-page","author":"Andrus Elbing (Beebilõust), saarlasest luuletaja ja räppar","images":[{"src":"beebiloust-crypti-laul.webp"}],"origin":"“Crypti laul”, kogu “Siin Beebilõust, tere! Häired pimelinna tänavalt (luuletusi 2004 - 2006)”, Epifanio, 2006.","tags":["avama","astuma","vaatama","röökima","kuulutama","nägema","liikuma","väljuma"],"genre":["luule"],"person":["Andrus E.","Beebilõust"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tänavad me vanemad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnad kodu ja kool on ka. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nCryptis me o'me paremad "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nSiin õe, venna hool on ka."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ei mingeid mänge enam, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmängudest saand on kuriteod. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nVarastame, röövime üha enam, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\npimelinna tondilossides meil agulipeod."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Me ei karda varjusi ööpimeduses, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nme ise ööpimeduse varjud oleme. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKits põgeneb imestuses, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmente appi karjub, kui me mööda agulit tuleme."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sest kitsed on me vaenlased, mendid ka "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja inimesed - meie vihkajad on nad. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKes pole meiega, pole kendid nad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmeist endist saand vihkajad ka."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hip hop on ainus armastus, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nillusioon, mis on mägedeni kõrguv "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkuid liiga hilja saabus vaimustus, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\npimelinnast meile juba saand on põrgu."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kuid täna on taevatähed mo õed vennad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnad mo vanemad on ka "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKui saabub tõehetk ja mulle helisevad hingekellad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nsiis nad mo luuleread ka."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"story-author","props":{":author":"author",":origin":"origin"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"details-wrapper","props":{"summary":"Mis mõtted tekkisid?"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Beebilõust “Mendid”: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eMM8e5hGXHk","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eMM8e5hGXHk"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“Tasapisi olen jõudnud äratundmisele, et maailm on selline nagu ta on ja et nii peabki olema. Varas varastab, mõrtsuk tapab, alkohoolik joob – asjad lihtsalt on niimoodi seatud. Meie ümber toimub Jumala mäng ja meie oleme vaid näitlejad selles. Hea ja halb kohtuvad ning sellest pingest juhtub kõik. Vahel harva, väga harva sünnivad aga imed. Ohtlik retsidivist, alkohoolik ja kogu Saaremaa hirm Andrus Elbing elas Tallinna Vanglas viieaastast karistust kandes üle vaimse ärkamise. Sünnipärase rütmiandega Elbing hakkas vanglas luuletama. See on tavaline, et pea iga vang kirjutab mõne luuletuse või teeb pliiatsijoonistuse, kuid Elbingu kirjutised torkasid oma ehedusega kohe silma. Ta mõtleb suurtes kujundites. Läbi tema suu kõneleb nägija, kes läbi vigade ja kannatuste on hakanud tunnetama elu kui igavest kulgemist, hinge lõpmatut eksistentsi ning seda, et oleme vaid ajutised külalised sellel võluval planeedil.”"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Nii kirjutab arhitekt ja kunstnik "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vilen Künnapu"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Beebilõusta esimese luulekogu eessõnas. Oled nõus, et asjad on maailmas nii seatud ja et oleme vaid näitlejad Jumala mängus? Kuidas põhjendad?"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"details-wrapper","props":{"summary":"Allikad","className":["text-sm"],"icon":"icon-park-outline:document-folder"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Luuletus: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Andrus Elbing"}]},{"type":"text","value":", “Crypti laul”, kogu “Siin Beebilõust, tere! Häired pimelinna tänavalt (luuletusi 2004 - 2006)”, Epifanio, 2006."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lõik eessõnast Beebilõusta luulekogule “Siin Beebilõust..”: "},{"typ